Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • Event
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Order, Reservation

    public abstract class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    This entity class provides all basic information from which the Order and Reservation entities can be extended from. This basic information includes Customer Name, Pax, and Table. Event class is an abstract class that requires returnType to be declared in any subclass (To identify between Order and Restaurant)
